@AGENTS.md

## Routing — every task

Before planning or editing anything:

1. Read `agent/skills/SKILL.md` and follow its decision table.
2. State which child skill you read next; follow leaf skills only when routed.
3. Edit skills only under `agent/skills/`; ask Foundry to sync renders after edits.

Rendered copies under `.claude/skills/` mirror the canonical tree — do not edit them by hand.
